  "profile": {
    "id": "u03_rohan",
    "user_name": "Rohan",
    "profession": "Bank PO aspirant",
    "mother_tongue": "Bengali",
    "interests": "Football, Bengali cinema, photography",
    "engagement": "chatty",
    "english_level": "A2",
    "personality": "enthusiastic, makes more grammar slips, talks about football a lot"
  },
  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Rohan, Manchester United fans don’t miss a match, how was the last one you watched?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It was 2-1 against Liverpool, right? I watched it last night. United played well but tired in the end. Oh, I was so excited! But I could not sleep well after that. The goal in the last minute was amazing, but I was too sleepy to enjoy much. How about you, watch any football?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That sounds intense. The excitement must have kept you buzzing. I get that, football can be so thrilling. Did you catch any other match recently?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "No, I didn’t watch any other match. Busy preparing for bank exam, so less time. But I still check the news about EPL. Oh, and I went to a local stadium last week. The atmosphere was amaaazing! But I got home late again, and again no sleep! 😅"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Got it, exam prep is a big focus. The local stadium visit sounds fun. What part of the match made you stay till the end?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The last goal was the main reason. It was a free kick, and the player curled it in the top corner. I was cheering so loud that the people around me looked at me like \"whoa!\" But yeah, I didn’t realize how late it was. I need to control my excitement, otherwise I can't study properly. Tumne koi khel dekha? 😅"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "What’s your favorite way to relax after a late match?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "After a match, I usually listen to music or watch some Bengali movies. Sometimes I take a walk, but mostly I just crash on the bed. But if I'm honest, I lie awake thinking about the match all over again. It’s fun, but not helpful for sleep! How do you relax?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I get that, reliving the action is part of the excitement. For me, a quiet evening with a book works best. What Bengali movie have you enjoying lately?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Oh, I loved \"Kichaka\" last month — the acting was so powerful! But honestly, most of my favorites are old ones like \"Antarneeyo\" or \"Chokher Bali.\" They are emotional, slow-paced, and perfect after a hectic day. Though, to be honest, I sometimes watch them even during exam prep! 😅 But football is better — no sleep, but more fun!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Got it, emotional stories and football both pull you in. That’s a great mix. Do you prefer newer Bengali movies or the old classics?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Old classics, mostly. New movies have good songs and stars, but the old ones have more depth. You know, like \"Antarneeyo\" — it's about love and society, very thought-provoking. But sometimes I get distracted while studying and open a movie instead of notes! 😅 How about you — any favorite type of movies?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Old classics have that timeless feel, I get it. What’s your favorite theme in them, love stories, historical tales, or something else?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Love stories, definitely. They show real emotions and struggles — you know, like in \"Chokher Bali\" or \"Komal Gandhar.\" They make me think, even if I’m not studying! 😅 But I should go now, need to revise some banking notes. Thanks for the chat, see you soon!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Love stories do leave a mark. Got it, banking notes need you now. See you soon, and keep that match day energy for study sessions too!\""
    }
  ],
